Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Esse anime não é recomendado para menores de 18 anos, e não é recomendado para pessoas sensíveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,115.667)}Aviso a prova de frescos:
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.51,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Será que não deveria\N ter um tamanho melhor?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.51,0:00:10.74,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso é bem comum.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.47,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Será que o Hinata vai\N gostar desse aqui...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.47,0:00:19.33,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Está tudo bem Bell,\N fique tranquila. 
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.36,0:00:22.16,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.15,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.01,0:00:31.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Desculpe pela demora.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.79,0:01:48.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Está muito quente!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.80,0:01:51.75,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Os verões neste mundo são brutais.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.63,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Neste ano, a situação está\N ainda pior do que o normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.34,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.41,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Está muito quente para caminhar!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.41,0:02:00.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Já estamos quase chegando em casa, só mais um pouquinho!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.28,0:02:04.31,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata! Por que está\N me evitando?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.89,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu não estou...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.75,0:02:10.60,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não posso contar a ela que estou muito atento a ela no momento!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.40,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hi-na-ta!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.94,0:02:20.94,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia... Você está\N me evitando!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.70,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você me surpreendeu\N agora, nada demais!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.15,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então me dê um abraço!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.15,0:02:29.20,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Faça com que fique ainda mais quente do que esse clima estúpido!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Talvez não devêssemos\N fazê-lo em público...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.34,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Por que não?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.66,0:02:37.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Vocês dois!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.09,0:02:40.84,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,No próximo dia de\N folga, vamos à praia!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.34,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Praia?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.28,0:02:48.31,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É o clima perfeito para isso, e acho que\N seria uma boa mudança de ritmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.31,0:02:54.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\fscx84\fscy95}Além disso, tenho certeza de que Sunohara ficaria \Nfeliz em vê-la usando um maiô bonito, Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.82,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Um maiô bonito...?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hi-na-ta!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,B-Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você fica muito sexy assim...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.91,0:03:08.50,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu não posso... Me conter!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.73,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você finalmente decidiu ser\N honesto consigo mesmo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.21,0:03:16.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Hinata! Agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.91,0:03:17.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Agora?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.95,0:03:21.49,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Se formos agora, já vai estar anoitecendo quando chegarmos.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Podemos ir quando?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.75,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Talvez no próximo domingo?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.75,0:03:28.12,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Precisamos comprar as\N roupas de banho.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.68,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Certifique-se de que\N esteja do meu lado!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,P-Por favor,\N espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,No fim das contas, acabamos chegando aqui...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.02,0:03:47.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O que você acha?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.44,0:03:49.02,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Está uma delícia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.75,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não é a raspadinha.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu estava falando\N do meu maiô.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você viu?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.42,0:04:01.76,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Dê uma boa... e uma longa... olhada.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell... Pare, muitas pessoas\N estão observando...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.91,0:04:06.64,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso não importa\N pra mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.17,0:04:10.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Escolhi esse maiô especialmente pra você, Hinata
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.21,0:04:14.38,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Pareço muito mais deliciosa do que essa raspadinha não é mesmo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.38,0:04:19.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas, você não é comida, então não sei se é tão “deliciosa”...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.74,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.19,0:04:24.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tem sabor de morango.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.67,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quer experimentar?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.30,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Pode ir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.66,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não, não se deixe levar!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você jurou que faria tudo certo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.32,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você não gosta do meu maiô...?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,N-Não, não é isso!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.63,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E o que você acha disso?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.51,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ahn?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não é do seu agrado?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.88,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E que tal este aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.12,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Me diga qual estilo\N você prefere.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.71,0:04:59.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu visto o que você\N quiser, Hinata.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.96,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Até mesmo algo\N desse tipo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.64,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Qual é o seu favorito?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.29,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Usar magia em uma\N praia lotada?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.44,0:05:14.54,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você está tentando irritar o Hinata novamente?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.54,0:05:16.50,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você tinha que vir junto...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quem é você para decidir\N como ele se sente?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Cecil-Chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.28,0:05:25.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell-Chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.76,0:05:28.26,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quer jogar vôlei de\N praia conosco?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.99,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Vôlei de praia?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.99,0:05:33.27,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Valeu. Talvez eu tenha \Numa queimadura de sol.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.79,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.64,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então, me deixe colocar um pouco\N de protetor solar em você!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.64,0:05:41.14,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Boa ideia! Ninguém gosta de uma queimadura de sol, não é mesmo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata! Você pode\N colocar protetor...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.28,0:05:46.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho que ir\N ao banheiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.06,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Vamos espalhar por aqui!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você está tensa, Cecil-Chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.00,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Trabalhar em um escritório é complicado.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.31,0:06:00.54,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sua pele é muito\N bonita, Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.47,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É tão brilhante \Nquanto uma joia!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.69,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim, Hinata falou \Na mesma coisa...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ele está me evitando, não está?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.23,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Estou incomodando...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Será que ele precisa\N de tempo?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.73,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.38,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sakura! Por que\N você fez isso?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.85,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você está ficando\N frouxa comigo, Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.67,0:06:23.97,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.97,0:06:26.84,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você e o Sunohara-Kun estão destinados um ao outro, certo?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.01,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Lembra o que você\N me contou antes?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,“Nunca mais sairei do lado do Hinata.”
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.31,0:06:39.14,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ter ouvido suas palavras \Nrealmente me inspirou!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.30,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.35,0:06:46.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Conhecendo o Sunohara-Kun, vai dar certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.53,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sakura...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.76,0:06:53.41,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, minha mão\N escorregou...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Está pingando em toda parte...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.25,0:06:57.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você pode limpá-lo?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.48,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você está bem? Vou \Npegar uma toalha!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.89,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sakura-Chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.19,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.95,0:07:16.40,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mariabell!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Pare de rir e venha ajudar!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.88,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Foi mal!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Saúde!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.37,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Cheira muito bem!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Parece estar uma delícia!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.68,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Só mais um pouquinho \Ne tudo já vai ficar pronto.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Um churrasco na praia...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.21,0:07:40.38,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso é muito bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.64,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Muito bem, vamos comer!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.61,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Que delícia!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.47,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Também temos camarão grelhado!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.61,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quer um pouco, Hinata?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.76,0:07:51.97,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.01,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O quê? ah, é, claro!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.62,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.78,0:08:04.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fique tranquila. Vou pegar para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.63,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não puxe com muita força!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.86,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Isso deve resolver o problema.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.48,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quem diria que essa\N coisa estava viva?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.34,0:08:19.20,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Onde estão Mariabell e o Hinata?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.23,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Calma, Bell. O que está acontecendo com você?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É você quem está agindo de\N forma estranha, Hinata
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.42,0:08:28.47,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É como se você estivesse evitando ficar sozinho comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso não é...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.55,0:08:30.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.39,0:08:35.46,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você não queria realmente\N ir à praia, nao é?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.51,0:08:40.36,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ou é isso, ou... você realmente não gosta mais de mim?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não, isso não...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.77,0:08:43.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu sei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.45,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ahn?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sei que você nunca \Nme odiaria, Hinata.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.43,0:08:51.13,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E mesmo que, de alguma forma, você me odiasse
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sei que você nunca, jamais,\N me evitaria dessa forma.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.15,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.41,0:09:01.77,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Percebo que algo o tem \Nincomodado ultimamente.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.77,0:09:06.23,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E posso dizer que tem\N algo a ver comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.86,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas ouça, Hinata...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.07,0:09:16.22,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não suporto ver você \Nsofrer por minha causa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você é todo o meu mundo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.90,0:09:22.58,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não... Eu me preocupo mais com você do que comigo mesmo.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.10,0:09:31.33,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Um pouco intenso, como sempre,\N mas também... gentil.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe, Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.84,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Agora me sinto melhor.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.87,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E sério?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.87,0:09:38.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.91,0:09:42.12,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Que bom. Fico feliz.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.65,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bem, é melhor voltarmos.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.39,0:09:54.86,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Que tal fazermos as pazes primeiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fazer as pazes, como...?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você me deixou preocupada, então... eu precisava de um pouco de tranquilidade.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.33,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não podemos, Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.33,0:10:06.08,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas você não me odeia, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu não odeio!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas eu... tenho que fazer as\N coisas da maneira certa!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, vamos fazer\N isso da maniera certa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.98,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Muito bem, vamos terminar!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Deveríamos tentar nadar\N mais longe juntos?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.25,0:10:30.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Façam uma corrida com \Nvocês até aquela rocha!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Preparar... vamos!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.49,0:10:39.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Nada surpreendente para um aventureiro que derrotou o Rei Demônio...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.94,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Também deveríamos ir!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso parece bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.37,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Qual é o problema, Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.18,0:10:53.12,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,A verdade é que... Tenho\N uma confissão a fazer.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.98,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.63,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu... não sei nadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.13,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ahn?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.94,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
